      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|><thought\n>It didn't help much. i've tried all that. it feels less like \"exhaustion\" and more like a permanent state. like the person who was actually alive is just gone. i'm just a walking corpse at this point, just waiting for the clock to run out. there's nothing left to rebuild.",
